gobblin.writer.commands

Class MySqlBufferedInserter

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.writer.commands.BaseJdbcBufferedInserter
      • gobblin.writer.commands.MySqlBufferedInserter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JdbcBufferedInserter

    public class MySqlBufferedInserter
extends BaseJdbcBufferedInserter
    The implementation of JdbcBufferedInserter for MySQL. This purpose of buffered insert is mainly for performance reason and the implementation is based on the reference manual http://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/5.0/en/insert-speed.html
